      <title>怀孕期间接种 COVID 疫苗可保护新生儿免于住院</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/09/27/g-s1-25069/getting-the-covid-vaccine-during-pregnancy-protects-newborns-from-hospitalization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[六个月以下的婴儿不能直接接种 COVID 疫苗。一项新研究发现，大多数因 COVID 住院的婴儿的母亲在怀孕期间没有接种疫苗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/09/27/g-s1-25069/getting-the-covid-vaccine-during-pregnancy-protects-newborns-from-hospitalization</guid>
